snippet.title: Nuketown Zombies Trailer - Official Call of Duty: Black Ops 2 Video
snippet.description: Some uninvited guests have arrived in the neighborhood. Fend off the undead horde in the ruins of Nuketown. Purchase the Season Pass and get the Nuketown Zombies bonus map. Available now on Xbox 360 with other platforms to follow. http://www.callofduty.com/blackops2/seasonpass
